---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Us | B & G Southwest - Delivering Excellence"
  description="Learn about B & G Southwest. Built on the logistics of reliability, our San Diego team delivers precision floor care and facility maintenance."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Organization",
      "@id": "https://bgsouthwest.com/#organization",
      "name": "B & G Southwest",
      "description": "Provider of commercial surface care, rooted in high-accountability delivery and logistics.",
      "url": "https://bgsouthwest.com",
      "logo": "https://bgsouthwest.com/img/van.png",
      "foundingDate": "2021",
      "knowsAbout": ["Commercial Floor Care", "VCT Stripping & Waxing", "Commercial Carpet Extraction", "Concrete Polishing"]
    }
    </script>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="hero" style="min-height: 50vh;">
    <img src="/img/hero-about.png" alt="Commercial surface care technicians using a tablet" class="hero-bg" fetchpriority="high">
    <div class="hero-gradient"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content" style="text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; padding-top: 4rem;">
        <h1 style="color: white;">The Gold Standard of Care</h1>
        <p style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #cbd5e1;">How a mindset rooted in delivery logistics evolved into San Diego's most precise surface care provider.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section-padding container">
      <div class="featured-section">
        <div class="featured-img-wrapper">
          <img src="/img/van.png" alt="B & G Southwest Commercial Fleet in San Diego" class="featured-img">
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2>Precision Operations for Surface Care</h2>
          <p>At B & G Southwest, we believe exceptional surface care starts with attention to detail, dependable service, and clear communication. Our team is committed to showing up on time, doing the job right, and making sure every client feels informed and supported from start to finish.</p>
          <p>We understand that in commercial environments, consistency matters. Floors, surfaces, and shared spaces reflect the standards of your business, which is why we approach every service with precision, care, and a strong sense of responsibility. No shortcuts, no guesswork, and no lack of follow-through.</p>
          <p>Our willingness to serve is at the center of everything we do. We take pride in being responsive, proactive, and easy to work with. Whether we are maintaining a high-traffic office, a retail space, or another commercial facility, our goal is to deliver reliable results while making the process smooth and stress-free for our customers.</p>
          <p>We also believe technology should make service better. That is why we leverage modern tools and systems to keep customers up to date, informed, and confident in the services they receive. From scheduling and service updates to communication and accountability, we use technology to create a better client experience and keep everyone in the know.</p>
          <p>At B & G Southwest Surface Care, we are committed to high standards, strong communication, and service you can count on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--bg-primary-dark); color: white;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 style="color: white; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">Our Experience & Credentials</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="card" style="background: var(--brand-navy-light); border: none;">
            <div class="card-icon">🧪</div>
            <h3 style="color: white;">Chemical Science Applied</h3>
            <p style="color: #cbd5e1;">We don't use multi-surface shortcuts. Whether mitigating pH levels on polished terrazzo or targeting protein stains in corporate carpets, our teams carry the specialized solutions required for strict material compatibility.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="background: var(--brand-navy-light); border: none;">
            <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
            <h3 style="color: white;">Embracing Automation</h3>
            <p style="color: #cbd5e1;">By integrating autonomous scrubbers (powered by advanced navigational AI) combined with human oversight, we provide consistent, overlapping maintenance that eliminates the risk of human fatigue on massive floor plans.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="background: var(--brand-navy-light); border: none;">
            <div class="card-icon">🎓</div>
            <h3 style="color: white;">Advanced Training</h3>
            <p style="color: #cbd5e1;">Led by technicians adhering to IICRC certification standards. Before a team member touches a burnisher or a hot-water extraction wand, they undergo rigorous, supervised technical onboarding.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
